00:16:06,805 --> 00:16:08,311
I understand that,
but I don't give a shit.

425
00:16:08,312 --> 00:16:09,345
Anyone but Brian.
- Louis--

426
00:16:09,347 --> 00:16:10,579
Katrina, listen to me.

427
00:16:10,581 --> 00:16:12,181
You asked for this
responsibility

