00:16:12,183 --> 00:16:13,983
so I gave it to you.
So now I am telling you

429
00:16:13,985 --> 00:16:16,018
to find a way to keep him.

430
00:16:17,221 --> 00:16:19,955
Okay, Louis.
I'll see what I can do.

